      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters (fluid properties, hemolysis model coefficients, boundary conditions) must have documented sources, uncertainty characterisation, and propagation through Monte Carlo or equivalent method at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was initiated but hemolysis model coefficients (alpha, beta exponents) were treated as fixed nominal values rather than uncertain inputs. Input uncertainty characterisation is incomplete; factor not fully assessed."
    },
