      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples (blood analogue batches) must be characterised for rheological properties with inter-batch variability quantified and propagated into validation uncertainty estimates.",
      "rationale": "Glycerol-water analogue properties were measured for a single batch. Inter-batch variability was not characterised and was not included in the experimental uncertainty budget. Factor not assessed at MRL 5 level."
